OL,7,FA County Durham mother accused of
OL,8,Fmurdering her son has sacked her legal
OL,9,Fteam the day after finishing giving
OL,10,Fevidence.
OL,12,FChristina Robinson is standing trial
OL,13,Fat Newcastle Crown Court accused of
OL,14,Fburning, caning and killing her three-
OL,15,Fyear-old son, Dwelaniyah, at their
OL,16,Fhome in County Durham. She denies
OL,17,Fmurder and child cruelty.
