OL,7,FRobinson gave evidence on Wednesday 13
OL,8,FMarch, and the following day, denying
OL,9,Fshaking the youngster to death or
OL,10,Fdeliberately burning him by putting
OL,11,Fhim in scalding water.
OL,13,FThe case was due to move onto the next
OL,14,Fstage on Friday but did not do so
OL,15,Fafter she decided to dispense with the
OL,16,Fservices of her barristers and
OL,17,Fsolicitors.
