OL,7,FTrial judge Mr Justice Garnham, who
OL,8,Fallowed Robinson to sit where her
OL,9,Fbarrister had been sitting, along with
OL,10,Fa dock officer, told the jury:
OL,11,F"There's been a development which has
OL,12,Fdelayed us which I need to tell you
OL,13,Fabout.
OL,15,F"Ms Robinson has decided to dispense
OL,16,Fwith the services of her barristers
OL,17,Fand solicitors. She's entitled to do
OL,18,Fthat.
