OL,3,CCounty Durham mother accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering her son, 3, sacks her legal
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,F"Nobody is required to have a legal
OL,8,Fteam representing them or have a
OL,9,Fparticular legal team representing
OL,10,Fthem. She decided to sack,
OL,11,Feffectively, her solicitors and
OL,12,Fbarristers.
OL,14,F"The question arises about how we
OL,15,Fproceed without them being here. We've
OL,16,Fdecided she should have the rest of
OL,17,Fthe day to consider her position and
OL,18,Fconsult with other people if she
OL,19,Fwishes before we go to the next stage
OL,20,Fof the case.
