OL,3,CCounty Durham mother accused of
OL,4,Cmurdering her son, 3, sacks her legal
OL,5,Cteam
OL,7,F"It means we can do nothing further
OL,8,Ftoday."
OL,10,FRobinson, 30, is accused of killing
OL,11,FDwelaniyah at the family home at
OL,12,FBracken Court, Ushaw Moor, Durham, in
OL,13,FNovember 2022.
OL,15,FThe defendant, who is a follower of
OL,16,Fthe Black Hebrew Israelites religion,
OL,17,Ftold the jury that prior to his death,
OL,18,Fshe hit him with a bamboo garden cane
OL,19,Fas a "correction" for playing with his
OL,20,Ffood.
