OL,7,FShe explained she was following a
OL,8,FYouTube video about the religion which
OL,9,Ftalked about the Bible encouraging the
OL,10,Fuse of the rod for discipline. But she
OL,11,Fhas denied violently shaking him,
OL,12,Fcausing a fatal brain injury, claiming
OL,13,Fhe collapsed while eating.
OL,15,FShe is also accused of deliberately
OL,16,Fscalding the little boy's legs and
OL,17,Fbuttocks in extremely hot water as a
OL,18,Fpunishment for soiling himself, around
OL,19,Fthree weeks before his death.
